&lt;h2 id=&#34;参考博文&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#参考博文&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; 参考博文：&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;[1] &lt;span class=&#34;exturl&#34; data-url=&#34;aHR0cHM6Ly9jbWFrZS5vcmcvY21ha2UvaGVscC9ib29rL21hc3RlcmluZy1jbWFrZS9jbWFrZS9IZWxwL2d1aWRlL3R1dG9yaWFsL2luZGV4Lmh0bWw=&#34;&gt;CMake Tutorial — Mastering CMake&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
